step.name: facName
step.script: var mapping;try { mapping = msg['row']['column1'].toString()+(!"".equals(msg['row']['column2'].toString()) ? " ("+msg['row']['column2'].toString()+")" : ""); }catch (e) { logger.error(e); mapping = '';}channelMap.put('facName', validate( mapping , '', new Array()));

step.name: pid
step.script: var mapping;try { mapping = msg['row']['column5'].toString(); }catch (e) { logger.error(e); mapping = '';}channelMap.put('pid', validate( mapping , '', new Array()));

step.name: softwareName
step.script: var mapping;try { mapping = $('facName')+" CPAD-Companion v.0.1"; }catch (e) { logger.error(e); mapping = '';}channelMap.put('softwareName', validate( mapping , '', new Array()));
